TODAY is the funeral of one of the most respected businessmen in Mzansi - Ntate Richard Maponya. Dignitaries from all over Mzansi, including president Cyril Rampahosa and former presidents Kgalema Motlante and Thabo Mbeki. Also in attendance is Rasta the Artist, who has displayed a painting of Ntate Maponya at the venue.  